content: I’ve been writing channel directions ever since I joined Jumpcut HQ. I’m gonna be writing 154th next. Right now though, even though I didn’t write it down… I want to record myself on how I talked to my therapists. I mostly ended up crying. Because when I talk about something it always seemed to hit my heart. The things that hit me a lot is losing people. And then me not doing much for them… So I feel like shit.
